jcolibri.cbrcore
Class TasksInstanceRegistry

java.lang.Object
  jcolibri.cbrcore.TasksInstanceRegistry
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class TasksInstanceRegistry
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Registry for currently created tasks instances. This object will hold all the current configured tasks, so also represents the operational status of the CBR applicaction being configured. This class implemetns a Singleton approach.
